Richard Carter (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Richard_Carter_(actor) 0 Richard Carter (born 11 December 1953 in Sydney, Australia) is an Australian actor who has appeared in several television series and independent films, and has also been a prominent voice-over artist. Some of Carter's filmography includes Rabbit-Proof Fence, Hating Alison Ashley. Babe: Pig in the City, Happy Feet Two, Our Lips Are Sealed - with Mary-Kate and Ashley Olsen and Mad Max: Fury Road.
